race.comment: BLAZING WARRIOR (4) was strongly fancied latest and proved too good with a half a length win at this track in a handy 22.80. Has a tricky draw to overcome but goes well at this distance. Recorded one of the quickest times on the card in scoring last start. Will go close again if runs up to latest. DIVA'S DELIGHT (1) comes off an average performance last start when eighth at Muswellbrook over 336m behind Zipping Deloris (20.26) in a Grade 4/5. The form from her last run is stacking up nicely. Has ability and can atone. KATIE'S QUICK (7) jumped well from the low draw and led all the way to score last start (23.05) at this track in a Grade 5 over 400m. Sure to be thereabouts. ALL ABOUT ARCHIE (8) is always a threat when he races at this track and distance.
